OL,3,C18-year-old named after body found in
OL,4,Criver
OL,6,FAn 18-year-old man who died in the
OL,7,FRiver Nith has been named as Benjamin
OL,8,FGlen from Dumfries.
OL,10,FHis body was discovered in the the
OL,11,FKingholm Road area of the town on
OL,12,FThursday (30th April).
OL,14,FEmergency services carried out
OL,15,Fsearches after receiving reports of a
OL,16,Fperson in the river shortly before 7pm
OL,17,Fon Thursday.
OL,19,FThe death is not being treated as
OL,20,Fsuspicious.
